meColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Hehe... to go on a date with Onii-chan. Unicorn… can’t wait...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Four Parallel Worlds": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["Bits of Courage &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">II LIVE「Four Parallel Worlds」</span><br>"]}, {"say": "At The Stardust Live Concert...", "narration": true}, {"bgm": "star", "bgName": "bg_story_star1", "say": "Wow! Stardust is so amazing!!!", "actorName": "Audience A", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Stardust, we love you, ahhhhh!!!", "actorName": "Audience B", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Haha...haha...", "actorName": "Audience C", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Thank you everyone for your support~ I can feel all your warmth~ Let’s rock’n roll!", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "L - O - V - E !! Star - dust !! L - O - V - E !! Star - dust !!", "actorName": "Everyone", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Everyone is so enthusiastic... What about Onii-chan?", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "（！！！！！）", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Onii-chan... looks so excited...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "And... so happy...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Thank you everyone~ Have Stardust’s songs been conveyed to your hearts?~ I look forward to the next time we meet!", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Woooooow!", "actorName": "Everyone", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ha~~ Stardust is absolutely the best~", "actorName": "Audience A", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Feels like... I’ve got no regrets anymore...", "actorName": "Audience B", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "No... I must survive until I can attend Stardust’s next concert!", "actorName": "Audience C", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "So this must be... the alluring power of music... Unicorn is getting pulled in...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Even Unicorn… is touched...by this concert...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Unicorn also wants to... make Onii-chan happy...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Unicorn's Annoyances": [{"sequence": ["Bits of Courage &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">III 「Unicorn’s Annoyances」</span><br>"]}, {"say": "A few days later…", "narration": true}, {"say": "Hmm... Unicorn… just can’t understand...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "During that concert... Onii-chan appeared as if he was bathing in a light of happiness...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "But that light didn’t come from Unicorn...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "(Shakes head furiously) No no... Unicorn just wants to make Onii-chan feel... happy.", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Hmm... what exactly can Unicorn do... to make Onii-chan... that happy...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Lady Stardust? Could it be... Unicorn can feel that she was the source of that light... the one bathed on Onii-chan...making him so happy.", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Onii-chan once said… “Don’t be afraid to ask”?", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Unicorn... wants to ask Lady Stardust...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Letter to Stardust": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["Bits of Courage &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">IV 「Letter to Stardust」</span><br>"]}, {"bgName": "bg_story_star2"}], "Echo of Stardust": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["Bits of Courage &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">V 「Echo of Stardust」</span><br>"]}, {"bgName": "bg_story_star3", "say": "Dear little Unicorn:", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I’m very happy to hear from Unicorn, I didn’t expect to have such a cute little fan.", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I can feel Unicorn's feelings from this letter of yours.", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "And, I can tell that Unicorn really like her Commander nii-chan~", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "The feelings you’re conveying in this letter has woken me up, certainly it cannot be wrong.", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Let me give Unicorn a little piece of advice.", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Bits of courage is the greatest form of magic, heehee~", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Take a brave step forward, let Unicorn's Commander nii-chan see a different you!", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I will cheer for you!~", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "From the singer who supports you, Stardust.", "actorName": "Stardust", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "A Change In Courage": [{"sequence": ["Bits of Courage &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">VI 「A Change In Courage」</span><br>"]}, {"say": "Wh-what should Unicorn do...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Even with the advice from Lady Stardust...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ugh…Unicorn is still nervous to express her feelings...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "And... such beautiful clothes... doesn’t really fit Unicorn... what if Onii-chan doesn’t like it...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Bits of Courage… is the greatest form of magic...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Yes, Unicorn will try her best!", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "A Little Magic": [{"sequence": ["Bits of Courage &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">VII 「A Little Magic」</span><br>"]}, {"say": "O-Onii-chan... before Unicorn says so, Onii-chan cannot open his eyes!", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ugh... it’s still like this...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Lady Stardust… please give Unicorn courage...", "actor": 206030, "actorName": "Unicorn", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "(Singing)...", "actor": 206031, "actorName": "Unicorn [Little Star Songstress]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Wh-what do you think? These clothes were gifted to Unicorn by Lady Stardust… as well as this song!", "actor": 206031, "actorName": "Unicorn [Little Star Songstress]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Lady Stardust said that this... will make Onii-chan happy...", "actor": 206031, "actorName": "Unicorn [Little Star Songstress]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Unicorn... has made an effort, right?", "actor": 206031, "actorName": "Unicorn [Little Star Songstress]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Hmm? O-Onii-chan?!!!", "actor": 206031, "actorName": "Unicorn [Little Star Songstress]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Sigh... thank goodness... Onii-chan is alright...", "actor": 206031, "actorName": "Unicorn [Little Star Songstress]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Huh? You fainted from being overly excited?", "actor": 206031, "actorName": "Unicorn [Little Star Songstress]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Onii-chan… (///)", "actor": 206031, "actorName": "Unicorn [Little Star Songstress]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Hehe... thank you... Onii-chan... Unicorn is so glad that she can make you happy. Unicorn feels satisfied, 